f
[x,x+1]
c_x \in [x,x+1]
f'(c_x) = f(x+1)-f(x)
c_x \to \infty \quad \Longleftrightarrow \quad x \to \infty
x \le c_x \le x+1
 \lim_{x \to \infty} f(x+1) - f(x) = \lim_{x \to \infty} f'(c_x) = \lim_{c_x \to \infty} f'(c_x) = 0. 
